description: Unique identifier for the esports team in the dataset.
Official name of the esports team or organization.
Total prize money earned by the team in US dollars across all competitions.
Total number of tournaments or competitions the team has participated in.
Name of the main game the team competes in (e.g., 'Dota 2', 'CS:GO', 'League of Legends').
Category or type of the game (e.g., 'MOBA', 'FPS', 'Battle Royale').
